synopsis.text: The Adventurers Guild receptionist job seemed like the perfect gig for Alina Clover, promising a serene and comfortable life. However, the reality is far from her dreams as she finds herself drowning in paperwork whenever adventurers fail to return from their missions. To escape the endless paperwork, Alina takes matters into her own hands and secretly embarks on defeating the monsters herself. Her covert actions earn her the nickname "Executioner," and she finally begins to enjoy her life. But when the elite troop Silver Sword spots her battling a fire dragon, their leader, Jade Skarde, becomes determined to recruit her. Will Alina maintain her secret life as a fighting receptionist, or will she join Silver Sword and embrace a new adventure? Dive into this thrilling tale of an ordinary receptionist's extraordinary double life!
